OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early low cloud will
OL,6,Fquickly clear then it will be another
OL,7,Fdry day with plenty of warm sunshine.
OL,8,FBecoming very warm in the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA warm and sunny evening. Dry
OL,11,Fwith long clear spells overnight but
OL,12,Fsome low loud will develop in the
OL,13,Fglens and feed through the Central
OL,14,FBelt.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FEarly low cloud will quickly
OL,17,Fclear. Otherwise another dry and sunny
OL,18,Fday and feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
